profile.profile_delete_warning:
Once your account is deleted, all of its resources and data will be
    permanently deleted.
profile.modal_delete_desc: Are you sure you want to delete your account ?
profile.modal_ask_pass: Please type your password to countinue
profile.browser_sessions_desc: Manage and log out your active sessions on other browsers and devices.
profile.browser_sessions_text:
If necessary, you may log out of all of your other browser sessions
    across all of your devices. Some of your recent sessions are listed
    below; however, this list may not be exhaustive. If you feel your
    account has been compromised, you should also update your password.
profile.two_fact_desc:
When two factor authentication is enabled, you will be prompted for a
    secure, random token during authentication. You may retrieve this
    token from your phone' s Google Authenticator application.
profile.two_fact_enabled: You have enabled two factor authentication.
profile.two_fact_disabled: You have not enabled two factor authentication.
profile.two_fact_finish_desc:
To finish enabling two factor authentication, scan the
    following QR code using your phone's authenticator
    application or enter the setup key and provide the generated
    OTP code.
profile.two_fact_enabled_desc:
Two factor authentication is now enabled. Scan the following QR code using your phone's authenticator application or
    enter the setup key.
profile.recovery_code_desc:
Store these recovery codes in a secure password manager. They
    can be used to recover access to your account if your two
    factor authentication device is lost.
profile.logout_broswer_sessions_desc:
Please enter your password to confirm you would like to log out of
    your other browser sessions across all of your devices.
profile.update_profile: Update your account's profile information and email address.
profile.resend_email_verification: Click here to re-send the verification email.
profile.email_verification_sent: A new verification link has been sent to your email address.
profile.update_profile_desc: Update your account's profile information and email address.
